tool_description: Get list of presign urls Amazon AWS S3 so you can upload multiple files all together. Our signed url endpoint simplifies your data uploading process. Instead of dealing with complicated permissions and authentication, you can generate presigned URLs effortlessly. These URLs act as secure keys, granting temporary access for your files to be uploaded to your AWS S3 bucket.
